title: 2021 Week 14 Preview + Holiday Party Recap
itunes:title: 2021 Week 14 Preview + Holiday Party Recap
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview every single upcoming game of Week 14, starting with the Monday night showdown between the Rams and Cardinals before the draft begins. Dan recaps the company holiday party and discusses a wardrobe malfunction.
